                              java.lang.String msgINFO,

                              boolean isFromEdgeAction,
                              java.lang.String nodeName,
                              boolean processTarget)
        Method responsible for creating a window to provide to the user a list with all PBDs. Only one of them needs to be selected.
        Parameters:
        pdbIds - pdb IDs
        msgINFO - output info
        taskMonitor - task monitor
        ptnSource - protein source
        ptnTarget - protein target
        processPDBfile - if true, process the pdbfile with an unknown chain, otherwise process pdbfile with a specific chain
        pdbFile - pdb file name
        HasMoreThanOneChain - indicates if there is more than one chain
        isFromEdgeAction - indicates if the method is called from edge action
        nodeName - node name
